## Getting Started

1. Fork the repository
2. Clone your fork: `git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/{{PROJECT_SLUG}}.git`
3. Install dependencies: `{{INSTALL_CMD}}`
4. Create a branch: `git checkout -b feature/your-feature-name`

